data.description: Back on the market- No fault to the seller. Welcome to your dream home nestled in a prime location, within moments of Rosedale Park, The Country Club Plaza, KU Med, and more. This meticulously updated residence is a testament to modern comfort and style. The home comes FULLY furnished, including TVs, dishes, and silverware. The interior has undergone an extensive transformation, boasting a plethora of upgrades. Enjoy new flooring and ceilings that create an inviting ambiance in every room. Fresh paint and textured walls lend a contemporary charm while new outlet covers add a polished finish.The bathroom has been completely revitalized with a new vanity, mirror, and lighting fixture, ensuring both elegance and functionality. All of the flooring has been leveled throughout the home, providing a consistent and smooth surface. Structural enhancements have been made, including the addition of steel support posts downstairs to reinforce and level the beams supporting the home, ensuring stability and longevity.The kitchen has been reimagined as a culinary haven, featuring raised and extended spaces adorned with all-new cabinets and stunning quartz countertops. A new microwave adds convenience to this sleek and modern space. Upstairs has been transformed into a serene bedroom retreat. Fresh railings, flooring, and lighting illuminate the area while new storage cubbies and closet shelves maximize organization and space utilization. Every room boasts new lighting fixtures. To enhance comfort in the living room, a fan was installed. Even the staircase has been meticulously redone, featuring new stairs, risers, and stained treads, radiating elegance and durability. The attention to detail continues with all-new doors throughout every room, elevating the overall aesthetic and functionality. Come check it our while you can!
